  "text": "Finally, the concept that IFNs can play a crucial role in T1D is also supported by numerous reports of T1D development following IFN-α therapy for viral hepatitis, often associated with other autoimmune disorders as well. Some of these reports have recently been reviewed [CITATION_1] . Altogether these aforementioned reports establish a strongly relevant basis for more extensive incorporation of inflammatory pathways in attempts to explain the pathogenesis of T1D and proposition of alternative treatment options.",
